data.description: Great set up for first time buyers or investors. Drive thru garage (Opens From Each End). Extended driveway on back for extra parking, RV or Boat Storage. Large covered patio area off back of garage. Nice size yard with mature trees. All tile floors, no carpet. So much potential in this little gem! Exterior of home is vinyl coated steel siding. Home is being sold AS IS.  New AC unit installed 10/2023
